{
  "stem": "6258.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he went to my Polish friend, brought all my dresses, and brought all my diaries, and everything, and wanted me-- wanted me to-- you know, to run away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was ready.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On one day, I was supposed to run away from the fliegerhorst.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I let my parents know about it and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then let's say I was supposed to run away on Thursday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on Tuesday, suddenly, the whole camp on fliegerhorst was evacuated to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So Hitler was much more quicker than we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I-- but I still had my papers there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she wrote me that my Polish friend said, let me know, because people were working outside of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was-- were coming there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That as soon I would be out of Plaszow, it's still not too late.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I found myself in the nachrichtengeratenlager, I thought this is just perfect.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know anyone here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have any bonds.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so many people run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will run away too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And especially this guy at the gate was-- knew me, because he was our neighbor from the street where I lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was this one who brought a letter to me from my Polish friend.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here, I will run away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then, the very first day when I arrived, I didn't want to talk to anyone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't want to get close to anyone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to have that feeling that I am leaving someone to be responsible for my running away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that who knows what is going to happen to them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as long as I don't know them and nothing, I don't feel so bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then, it ate my heart, this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
